MALACAÑANG Manila

PROCLAMATION NO. 604

AMENDING PROCLAMATION NO. 20, S. 1926 WHICH RESERVED CERTAIN PARCEL OF LAND SITUATED IN THE CITY OF DAVAO FOR WIRELESS STATION PURPOSES BY EXCLUDING FROM ITS OPERATION THE UNUTILIZED PORTIONS OF THE LAND EMBRACED THEREIN AND DECLARING THE SAME OPEN FOR DISPOSITION IN FAVOR OF THE ACTUAL OCCUPANTS UNDER THE PROVISIONS OF THE PUBLIC LAND ACT, AS AMENDED

Upon the recommendation of the Secretary of Environment and Natural Resources, and by virtue of the powers vested in me by law, I, GLORIA MACAPAGAL-ARROYO , President of the Republic of the Philippines, do hereby amend Proclamation No. 20 dated March 23, 1926 which reserved certain parcel of land situated the City of Davao, Island of Mindanao for wireless station purposes, by excluding from its operation the unutilized portions of the land embraced therein and declaring the same open for disposition under the provisions of the Public Land Act, as amended, subject to private rights, if there be any, which portions of land are more particularly described as follows:

