An Inter-Agency Committee (LIAC), composed of representatives from HUDCC as Chair, the City Government of Davao, DENR, PCUP, and the people’s organization in the area as members is hereby created to immediately prepare the implementing rules and regulations (IRR) of this proclamation.

Except in favor of the government or any of its branches or agencies, all land disposed under this Proclamation shall not be subject to alienation and encumbrance for a term of ten years from the issuance of the title in case of sale or execution of contract in case of lease, nor shall they become liable to the satisfaction of any debt contracted prior to the expiration of said period, but the improvements of the land may be mortgaged to qualified persons, associations or corporations.

IN WITNESS WHEREOF , I have hereunto set my hand and caused the seal of the Republic of the Philippines to be affixed.

DONE in the City of Manila, this 13 th day of April , in the year of Our Lord, Two Thousand and Four.

(Sgd.) GLORIA MACAPAGAL-ARROYO

By the President: (Sgd.) ALBERTO G. ROMULO Executive Secretary

